<h2> Approved dl excise</h2>
The Council of Ministers, as it learns, has approved three schemes of Dl in the fiscal field which contain, among the various prescriptions, changes in the matter of biennial prior arrangement - such as the stop to the forfeit regimes and the postponement to 30 September > for membership - and the revision of the fiscal rates with a rebalance in 5 years between oil and petroleum > Approval therefore the single text scheme the Dl scheme on the revision of the excise provisions (Definite examination); the scheme of supplementary and corrective provisions concerning tax obligations, agreed biennial estimate, > tax justice and tax sanctions (preliminary examination).
